{"tid":93041,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"(無圖）我偷影左朋友電話入面d 資料","createTime":"2017-01-24T06:00:21.000Z","updateTime":"2017-01-24T07:50:23.000Z","uid":24585,"like":1,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"650d8532a18f51aab44e2583191b9c56dc466fbb","tid":93041,"uid":24585,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-24T06:00:21.000Z","msg":"是咁的 上年12月頭我同我朋友訂酒店 出發前幾日我問過佢比到3500蚊我未（酒店+之前差我既整車錢）佢話可以既 點知到機場問佢攞時佢話下個月先比到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 之後佢係一個我都係入面既群到講話想約人去食放題同睇電影 咁我就問佢下個月幾時比到我 佢話要等佢15號出糧先 不過未必比得曬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 仲笑笑口咁講<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  然後我有日特燈偷睇佢iPhone 個4位密碼 然後夜晚佢沖涼我就偷影佢電話入面屋企人既資料 打算到2月尾都未還比我既就send sms 比佢啊媽同佢講返呢件事<br />\n<br />\n大家覺得我應唔應該咁做"},{"pid":"138f47ecfe116ecafb86cf87ae305d29def4653c","tid":93041,"uid":41527,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-24T06:19:43.000Z","msg":"不應該"},{"pid":"0aef7e90ed75df928613cec50e1256613b190964","tid":93041,"uid":53830,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-24T06:24:09.000Z","msg":"如果佢一拖再拖唔打算還，<br />\n同埋你唔想再同佢做朋友，<br />\n你咪咁做<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bf4b30f21e7b61377a4463638859a4e057f07d74","tid":93041,"uid":24585,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-24T06:34:13.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>不應該</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bec5cac1f8c5481f3fa6faee68e579d341e7c4ba","tid":93041,"uid":24585,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-24T06:34:27.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>如果佢一拖再拖唔打算還，<br />\n同埋你唔想再同佢做朋友，<br />\n你咪咁做<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e1af0dc0a520ca149c634d4c079d3f81ec51